body:
Hi,

Trying to run this piece of code (as part of a testbench, not bringing here the whole files bunch).
Verilator returns this error, which i am not sure how to resolve, please advice. 

```
%Error: generator.sv:3:5: Class parameter type without default value is never given value (IEEE 1800-2023 6.20.1): 'T'
    3 |     mailbox gen2drv;
      |     ^~~~~~~
%Error: generator.sv:5:19: Class parameter type without default value is never given value (IEEE 1800-2023 6.20.1): 'T'
    5 |     function new (mailbox gen2drv_init);
```

The relevant code:
```
class generator;
    transaction trans;
    mailbox gen2drv;

    function new (mailbox gen2drv_init);
        this.gen2drv = gen2drv_init;
    endfunction

    task main();
        repeat(2)
        begin
            trans = new();
            trans.randomize();
            trans.display("Generator signals");
            gen2drv.put(trans);
        end
    endtask
endclass
```

